OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1779455476
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 5 Jun to Fri 19 Jun
OL,6,FHigh pressure is likely to bring fair
OL,7,Fweather for most at first. Rain and
OL,8,Fshowers are still possible at times,
OL,9,Fmainly across Northern Ireland and
OL,10,FScotland. As we head towards mid-June,
OL,11,Fmore mixed conditions are likely with
OL,12,Fspells of rain and showers. Drier
OL,13,Fweather is expected between any bouts
OL,14,Fof wetter weather. These drier
OL,15,Finterludes will tend to last longer
OL,16,Facross the south and east of England.
OL,17,FTemperatures are most likely to be
OL,18,Fnear or slightly above average
OL,19,Foverall, with some warm or very warm
OL,20,Fweather possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
